<div class="body">
  <p>Comment was approved by <a href='https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/profile/<%= @moderator.username %>'><%= @moderator.username %></a> after entering moderation queue <%= time_ago_in_words(@comment.created_at) %> ago and is now visible in the <a href='https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/dashboard'>Public Lab research feed</a>. Thanks for helping to keep Public Lab a welcoming and spam-free space!</p>

  <p>Now, reach out to welcome the new community member; thank them, just say hello, or help them revise/format their post in the comments. You can read and respond to the post here: https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %><%= @comment.node.path %></p>

  <p>View <a href="https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/profile/<%= @comment.author.name %>"><%= @comment.author.name %>'s profile</a></p>

  <hr />

  <div class="footer">

    <p>You received this email because you are <a href="https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/wiki/moderation">a Public Lab community moderator</a></p>

    <p>To discuss spam/abuse, forward this to <a href="mailto:moderators@<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>">comment-moderators@<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %></a></p>
  </div>

<%= @footer %>

</div>
<style media="screen">
  .body {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  }
  .footer {
    color: #aaa;
  }
</style>
